    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2026-04-05"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "1961-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>, <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/76fd0da7-1e91-4ad3-a88b-8c2f89b0b2e0> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__48344.
