_:b0__5659 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((9.32 69.42,29.80 69.42,29.80 53.87,9.32 53.87,9.32 69.42))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/c9e0e8f2-bdab-4d86-b84e-9c05051e152d> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/kundtjanst_smhi.se>;
