    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/277> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/4/resource/16>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/TopicCategory/transportation>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/8641>;
