    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/a2e5d087-8576-4028-a6c2-1e979c75e2dc>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-05T06:27:17.412Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#14c52e60fa55bbba47691a5df2a1048d> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/a2e5d087-8576-4028-a6c2-1e979c75e2dc> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "statistik", "årsbok";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/NEVER>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "a2e5d087-8576-4028-a6c2-1e979c75e2dc";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Malmö stads statistiska årsbok innehåller statistik om bland annat Malmös befolkning, näringsliv och bostadsmarknad. Publikationerna innehåller ��ven statistik om stadens finanser och verk samt kartor över de olika geografiska indelningarna som används."@sv, "The City of Malmö's statistical yearbook contains statistics on Malmö's\npopulation, business and housing market, among other things. The publications\nalso contain statistics on the city's finances and works, as well as maps of\nthe various geographical divisions used.\n\n"@en, "Malmø Kommunes statistiske årbog indeholder blandt andet statistik om Malmøs\nbefolkning, erhvervsliv og boligmarked. Publikationerne indeholder også\nstatistik om byens finanser og arbejder samt kort over de forskellige anvendte\ngeografiske opdelinger.\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__7743.
_:b0__7743 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
